gstat.premade.uno

Class UnoCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • gstat.premade.uno.UnoCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Card

    public class UnoCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements Card
    This class is a card for the game of UNO. It tells the color and number of the Uno Card. It implements the card interface to it can be utilized by the hand class.
    Author:
    Camden Voigt
